Kim Baek-du. Awak nak ke mana?

240
00:18:04,708 --> 00:18:06,752
Saya ada hal mustahak.

241
00:18:07,461 --> 00:18:08,295
Tunggu.

242
00:18:09,379 --> 00:18:11,256
Kenapa tak dengar cakap saya?

243
00:18:12,341 --> 00:18:13,675
Awak cakap apa?

244
00:18:13,759 --> 00:18:16,261
Saya cakap jangan guna teknik biasa.

245
00:18:16,345 --> 00:18:17,763
Awak guna banyak kali.

246
00:18:19,431 --> 00:18:22,184
Saya tak berniat…

247
00:18:22,267 --> 00:18:23,185
Cara itu berkesan.

248
00:18:24,645 --> 00:18:25,479
Apa?

249
00:18:25,562 --> 00:18:27,481
Selama ini, saya terlupa

250
00:18:27,564 --> 00:18:29,650
itu cara awak bergusti ssireum.

251
00:18:31,235 --> 00:18:34,696
Sebab itulah awak digelar 
bakat luar biasa ssireum.

252
00:18:34,780 --> 00:18:36,323
Saya terlupa yang dulu

253
00:18:38,075 --> 00:18:39,827
saya sangat cemburukan awak.

254
00:18:43,997 --> 00:18:46,250
Apa pun, perlawanan awak sangat hebat.

255
00:18:47,584 --> 00:18:48,460
Okey.

256
00:18:52,089 --> 00:18:52,923
Jin-su.

257
00:18:54,550 --> 00:18:55,384
Apa?

258
00:18:56,468 --> 00:18:57,344
Terima kasih.

259
00:19:00,597 --> 00:19:01,473
Jumpa lagi.

260
00:19:12,901 --> 00:19:16,196
Pemenang Pertandingan Ssireum 
Kanak-kanak Kebangsaan 2002

261
00:19:16,280 --> 00:19:19,658
ialah Kim Baek-du 
dari Sekolah Rendah Geosan.

262
00:19:20,367 --> 00:19:22,202
- Tahniah, Baek-du! 
- Syabas!

263
00:19:22,286 --> 00:19:24,121
- Sayang Baek-du! 
- Syabas.

264
00:19:24,788 --> 00:19:26,790
- Awak sangat hebat! 
- Syabas.

265
00:19:31,795 --> 00:19:33,005
Dia sangat berbakat.

266
00:19:33,088 --> 00:19:35,007
Syabas, Baek-du!

267
00:19:37,843 --> 00:19:39,178
Budak tak guna.

268
00:19:43,974 --> 00:19:45,267
Du-sik.

269
00:19:48,854 --> 00:19:50,105
Oh Du-sik!

270
00:19:55,319 --> 00:19:57,404
Du-sik!

271
00:19:58,113 --> 00:20:00,324
Oh Du-sik!

272
00:20:01,658 --> 00:20:02,951
Dia tak balik lagi?

273
00:20:03,785 --> 00:20:05,454
Oh Du…

274
00:20:06,747 --> 00:20:07,956
Awak dah gilakah?

275
00:20:08,040 --> 00:20:10,042
Awak buat apa lewat malam begini?

276
00:20:10,125 --> 00:20:11,335
Awak dari mana?

277
00:20:11,418 --> 00:20:12,294
- Saya… 
- Diam.

278
00:20:12,377 --> 00:20:14,129
Saya panggil awak dari sini…

279
00:20:14,213 --> 00:20:15,214
Hei, tunggu.

280
00:20:15,297 --> 00:20:16,381
Hei.

281
00:20:28,352 --> 00:20:31,855
Awak buat apa di rumah saya 
tengah-tengah malam begini?

282
00:20:33,190 --> 00:20:35,651
Saya tak ada masa nak bersedih sebab awak.

283
00:20:36,443 --> 00:20:38,528
- Awak asyik mengacau. 
- Mana ada.

284
00:20:38,612 --> 00:20:40,239
Saya tak buat apa-apa pun.

285
00:20:40,322 --> 00:20:41,531
Apa awak cakap?

286
00:20:42,699 --> 00:20:44,660
Awak nampak macam orang mabuk.

287
00:20:45,702 --> 00:20:47,287
Awak minum arak?

288
00:20:48,080 --> 00:20:49,831
Ya. Kenapa?

289
00:20:49,915 --> 00:20:52,709
Awak cakap awak tak boleh minum arak.

290
00:20:53,377 --> 00:20:55,462
Awak tak ingat apa-apa selepas minum.

291
00:20:55,545 --> 00:20:58,006
Ya, betul.

292
00:20:58,090 --> 00:21:01,468
Jadi kenapa awak minum?

293
00:21:01,551 --> 00:21:04,972
- Hati-hatilah sikit… 
- Sebab saya geram!

294
00:21:06,306 --> 00:21:07,391
Apa?

295
00:21:07,474 --> 00:21:09,268
Hei, sampai hati awak

296
00:21:10,018 --> 00:21:13,313
tiba-tiba balik ketika perlawanan 
masih berlangsung?

297
00:21:13,855 --> 00:21:15,899
Saya sangka awak ada di sana.

298
00:21:17,818 --> 00:21:19,987
Ada hal penting hari ini, jadi…

299
00:21:20,070 --> 00:21:21,321
Mesej saya pun

300
00:21:21,405 --> 00:21:24,491
awak tak balas. 
Awak baca saja, tapi tak balas.

301
00:21:27,995 --> 00:21:30,580
Awak tahu tak? Tak balas mesej orang

302
00:21:31,373 --> 00:21:33,709
adalah satu jenayah.

303
00:21:37,004 --> 00:21:38,046
Okey.

304
00:21:39,756 --> 00:21:41,758
Saya penjenayah.

305
00:21:41,842 --> 00:21:43,677
- Saya penjenayah. 
- Ya.

306
00:21:44,636 --> 00:21:45,846
Awak tahu tak?

307
00:21:46,346 --> 00:21:48,473
Saya buat perangai

308
00:21:49,850 --> 00:21:52,853
biasanya sebab awak. Awak tahu tak?

309
00:21:54,229 --> 00:21:55,355
Jadi…

310
00:21:56,356 --> 00:21:57,774
berapa banyak awak minum?

311
00:21:58,358 --> 00:21:59,401
Awak minum banyak?

312
00:22:00,944 --> 00:22:02,571
Segelas bir saja.

313
00:22:03,780 --> 00:22:06,283
Tapi tadi saya cuma

314
00:22:07,284 --> 00:22:10,162
nak tenangkan fikiran saya.

315
00:22:15,417 --> 00:22:19,504
Kalau minum segelas bir, 
fikiran awak tenang?

316
00:22:19,588 --> 00:22:22,674
Awak buat saya rasa bersalah.

317
00:22:23,258 --> 00:22:24,760
Entahlah.

318
00:22:24,843 --> 00:22:26,803
Aduh, seksanya.

319
00:22:26,887 --> 00:22:28,764
Kepala saya sakit dan…

320
00:22:28,847 --> 00:22:30,599
- Hei, hati-hati. 
- Aduh.

321
00:22:30,682 --> 00:22:32,893
- Sakitnya. 
- Kenapa dengan awak?

322
00:22:34,227 --> 00:22:36,438
Hei.

323
00:22:38,023 --> 00:22:40,734
Awak tahu tak saya dapat nombor berapa?

324
00:22:40,817 --> 00:22:42,152
Cuba teka.

325
00:22:42,235 --> 00:22:44,112
- Teka. 
- Nombor empat?

326
00:22:46,239 --> 00:22:47,491
Hebat, bukan?

327
00:22:48,158 --> 00:22:49,534
Ya, hebat.

328
00:22:50,827 --> 00:22:51,787
Sudah. Jom balik.

329
00:22:51,870 --> 00:22:53,830
Tunggu.

330
00:22:54,956 --> 00:22:55,874
Boleh awak…

331
00:22:56,625 --> 00:22:58,543
Boleh awak buat lagi?

332
00:22:59,086 --> 00:23:00,212
Apa?

333
00:23:00,295 --> 00:23:02,589
"Awak bagus, awak hebat."

334
00:23:02,672 --> 00:23:05,425
Pujilah saya lagi. Saya nak dengar.

335
00:23:10,097 --> 00:23:12,641
Aduhai, awak memang…

336
00:23:14,434 --> 00:23:15,936
Baiklah.

337
00:23:16,561 --> 00:23:20,816
Awak hebat sekali hari ini. 
Awak sangat mengagumkan.

338
00:23:22,692 --> 00:23:23,735
Lagi?

339
00:23:25,737 --> 00:23:27,447
Pujilah lagi.

340
00:23:27,531 --> 00:23:28,990
- Lagi? 
- Ya.

341
00:23:30,992 --> 00:23:32,035
Saya rasa…

342
00:23:33,161 --> 00:23:36,957
saya nampak diri awak yang dulu. 
Saya suka.

343
00:23:37,707 --> 00:23:39,876
Diri saya yang dulu?

344
00:23:39,960 --> 00:23:40,836
Ya.

345
00:23:41,545 --> 00:23:45,674
Dulu awak cuma minat ssireum. 
Awak tak peduli

346
00:23:45,757 --> 00:23:47,467
kalau awak menang atau kalah.

347
00:23:50,053 --> 00:23:51,847
Bila, ya?

348
00:23:52,389 --> 00:23:54,182
Saya rasa waktu darjah tiga.

349
00:23:54,266 --> 00:23:56,893
Tak lama selepas awak 
mula belajar ssireum.

350
00:23:58,353 --> 00:24:01,648
Awak lawan budak darjah enam 
yang berbadan besar.

351
00:24:01,731 --> 00:24:04,276
Tak masuk akal betul.

352
00:24:04,359 --> 00:24:06,987
Awak kalah teruk.

353
00:24:07,779 --> 00:24:12,701
Saya sangka awak akan berkurung 
dalam bilik air dan menangis,

354
00:24:12,784 --> 00:24:14,286
tapi saya silap.

355
00:24:14,369 --> 00:24:16,663
Sambil tersenyum lebar, awak kata,

356
00:24:17,914 --> 00:24:20,542
"Du-sik, saya seronok sangat.

357
00:24:20,625 --> 00:24:22,627
Saya nak lawan dia lagi."

358
00:24:25,881 --> 00:24:29,759
Aduhai, saya memang kuat temberang 
semasa kecil.

359
00:24:29,843 --> 00:24:31,469
Itu bukan temberang.

360
00:24:31,553 --> 00:24:33,513
Saya kagum dengan awak.

361
00:24:33,597 --> 00:24:36,766
Saya rasa itu buat awak nampak matang.

362
00:24:36,850 --> 00:24:39,853
Saya rasa saya belanja 
awak makan sate sebelum balik.

363
00:24:43,523 --> 00:24:45,108
Dulu pun,

364
00:24:46,318 --> 00:24:50,697
saya rasa awak akan jadi 
pemain ssireum yang berjaya dewasa nanti.

365
00:24:52,782 --> 00:24:55,785
Tapi sekarang, badan saja besar, 
tapi bengap.

366
00:25:05,045 --> 00:25:06,546
Tapi awak tahu tak?

367
00:25:08,089 --> 00:25:11,843
Saya suka kejohanan hari ini 
bukan sebab awak dapat nombor empat,

368
00:25:13,428 --> 00:25:16,681
tapi sebab awak seronok 
berlawan macam dulu.

369
00:25:17,974 --> 00:25:21,186
Awak boleh cuba lagi lain kali.

370
00:25:21,269 --> 00:25:22,979
Usaha tangga kejayaan.

371
00:25:23,730 --> 00:25:25,398
Dan saya boleh jamin,

372
00:25:25,482 --> 00:25:28,235
kalau awak kekal yakin begini, 
awak pasti boleh

373
00:25:28,318 --> 00:25:30,445
jadi jaguh dalam perlawanan seterusnya.

374
00:25:30,528 --> 00:25:32,572
Siapa nama budak itu?

375
00:25:32,656 --> 00:25:34,074
Ya, Lim Dong-seok.

376
00:25:34,157 --> 00:25:36,201
Dia taklah hebat mana…

377
00:25:39,079 --> 00:25:40,914
Dia biasa-biasa saja.

378
00:25:43,416 --> 00:25:45,794
Hei, mata awak…

379
00:25:46,419 --> 00:25:48,505
Kenapa awak pandang saya begitu?

380
00:26:09,693 --> 00:26:10,735
Hei!

381
00:26:11,528 --> 00:26:13,113
Awak buat apa?

382
00:26:14,864 --> 00:26:16,700
Saya cium awaklah.

383
00:26:22,372 --> 00:26:24,124
Hei, Kim Baek-du!

384
00:26:40,598 --> 00:26:42,767
- Tak guna. 
- "Tak guna"?

385
00:26:46,688 --> 00:26:51,026
Ibu buat saya terkejut saja.

386
00:26:52,861 --> 00:26:55,322
Saya nak bangun sambil tersenyum 
setiap pagi.

387
00:26:55,405 --> 00:26:58,700
Jadi janganlah tayang muka 
dekat-dekat dengan muka saya.

388
00:26:58,783 --> 00:27:01,995
- Hormat sikit ibu, budak tak guna. 
- Janganlah.

389
00:27:02,078 --> 00:27:02,912
Hei.

390
00:27:03,747 --> 00:27:05,165
Pukul berapa kamu balik?

391
00:27:05,999 --> 00:27:08,251
Malam tadi? Pukul berapa saya balik?

392
00:27:09,169 --> 00:27:11,671
Budak ini… Kamu minum arak lagi?

393
00:27:12,380 --> 00:27:13,214
Arak?

394
00:27:14,382 --> 00:27:17,635
Saya cakap saya tak nak minum, 
tapi Jin-su tetap

395
00:27:17,719 --> 00:27:19,387
nak tuangkan arak untuk saya…

396
00:27:19,471 --> 00:27:21,264
Kamu tak perlu minum!

397
00:27:21,348 --> 00:27:23,058
Kamu dah tahu apa kesannya.

398
00:27:25,602 --> 00:27:27,687
Jangan minum arak lagi.

399
00:27:27,771 --> 00:27:30,398
- Kalau tidak, siap kamu. 
- Yalah, saya faham.

400
00:27:33,610 --> 00:27:35,111
Hei. Nanti dulu.

401
00:27:35,195 --> 00:27:36,279
- Kenapa? 
- Nanti.

402
00:27:36,905 --> 00:27:38,239
Apa ini?

403
00:27:38,323 --> 00:27:39,324
Apa?

404
00:27:39,824 --> 00:27:41,451
Kenapa dahi kamu merah sangat?

405
00:27:41,534 --> 00:27:42,994
Kenapa dengan dahi saya?

406
00:27:44,162 --> 00:27:47,290
Ini bekas tapak tangankah? 
Ada orang pukul kamu?

407
00:27:47,374 --> 00:27:48,249
Mana ada.

408
00:27:48,333 --> 00:27:49,876
- Hei… 
- Rasanya tak ada.

409
00:27:49,959 --> 00:27:51,628
- Ya Tuhan. 
- Kenapa?

410
00:27:51,711 --> 00:27:53,797
Siapa yang buat?

411
00:27:53,880 --> 00:27:57,133
Siapa buat dahi anak ibu berbekas?

412
00:27:57,217 --> 00:27:59,177
- Tak apalah. 
- Aduhai.

413
00:27:59,260 --> 00:28:00,428
Tak apa.

414
00:28:00,512 --> 00:28:02,389
- Apa… 
- Tak apa, tak sakit pun.

415
00:28:02,472 --> 00:28:04,599
- Jangan risau. 
- Geramnya ibu.

416
00:28:04,682 --> 00:28:06,101
Tak apa. Ibu pergilah.

417
00:28:06,184 --> 00:28:08,353
- Sudahlah. Mari sarapan. 
- Okey.

418
00:28:09,354 --> 00:28:11,481
Cepat. Ibu bubuh ubat di dahi kamu.

419
00:28:11,564 --> 00:28:13,566
Okey. Saya baru saja bangun.

420
00:28:28,331 --> 00:28:29,290
Apa?

421
00:28:29,916 --> 00:28:31,459
Betullah.

422
00:28:32,544 --> 00:28:34,629
Siapa yang buat?

423
00:28:45,932 --> 00:28:47,934
Selamat pagi, Yu-gyeong.

424
00:28:49,853 --> 00:28:50,729
Yu-gyeong.

425
00:28:51,730 --> 00:28:53,732
Kenapa dengan muka awak?

426
00:28:54,524 --> 00:28:55,400
Apa?

427
00:28:56,943 --> 00:28:58,069
Awak tak tidurkah?

428
00:28:59,154 --> 00:29:01,448
Awak nampak buruk sikit hari ini.

429
00:29:01,990 --> 00:29:02,824
Apa?

430
00:29:02,907 --> 00:29:04,451
Awak nampak buruk.

431
00:29:18,423 --> 00:29:20,341
Buruk, bukan? Betul tak?

432
00:29:21,217 --> 00:29:23,386
Awak buat apa dengan Baek-du?

433
00:29:23,970 --> 00:29:25,221
Apa maksud awak?

434
00:29:26,556 --> 00:29:28,349
Siapa kata kami berjumpa semalam?

435
00:29:28,433 --> 00:29:30,727
Dia buat bising di sini malam tadi

436
00:29:30,810 --> 00:29:32,479
dan awak terus bawa dia lari.

437
00:29:33,021 --> 00:29:34,647
Tak ada apa-apa berlaku!

438
00:29:35,565 --> 00:29:39,110
Mana mungkin ada apa-apa berlaku 
antara kami.

439
00:29:39,194 --> 00:29:41,654
Awak dah mula merepek lagi.

440
00:29:48,369 --> 00:29:50,246
Kenapa dia marah sangat?

441
00:30:01,299 --> 00:30:02,801
Saya nampak tak terurus.

442
00:30:03,718 --> 00:30:05,929
Ini semua salah Kim Baek-du.

443
00:30:14,229 --> 00:30:18,191
Dan dia takkan ingat pun.

444
00:30:44,801 --> 00:30:46,010
Hei, Oh Du-sik.

445
00:30:46,678 --> 00:30:48,471
Kenapa buat muka begitu?

446
00:30:48,555 --> 00:30:49,681
Gilakah?

447
00:30:50,223 --> 00:30:51,808
Jangan ingat lagi!

448
00:31:04,821 --> 00:31:06,406
Ganasnya dia.

449
00:31:40,565 --> 00:31:43,401
Saya kaya. Saya ada banyak duit.

450
00:31:43,484 --> 00:31:46,446
Biar saya belanja hari ini. 
Mari ikut saya.

451
00:31:46,529 --> 00:31:48,948
Belanja kami di kedai runcit?

452
00:31:49,449 --> 00:31:52,660
Bising betul bunyi duit syiling.

453
00:31:52,744 --> 00:31:54,996
Peganglah poket kamu ketika berjalan.

454
00:31:55,788 --> 00:31:58,875
Kamu dapat hadiah duit syilingkah?

455
00:31:58,958 --> 00:32:00,126
- Peliknya. 
- Helo.

456
00:32:00,668 --> 00:32:02,170
- Seni bela diri… 
- Helo?

457
00:32:02,253 --> 00:32:04,255
Penatnya abang.

458
00:32:04,339 --> 00:32:05,924
- Kamu rupanya. 
- Helo.

459
00:32:06,007 --> 00:32:07,842
- Helo. 
- Panasnya.

460
00:32:07,926 --> 00:32:09,093
Cuaca panas hari ini.

461
00:32:09,177 --> 00:32:12,013
Beli yang paling mahal. 
Kamu belanja, bukan?

462
00:32:12,096 --> 00:32:13,848
Berapa suhu hari ini?

463
00:32:13,932 --> 00:32:15,433
Panasnya.

464
00:32:15,516 --> 00:32:18,019
- Ini duitnya. 
- Terima kasih.

465
00:32:18,102 --> 00:32:20,063
Nah, ambillah.

466
00:32:20,146 --> 00:32:20,980
Nah.

467
00:32:21,522 --> 00:32:23,608
- Ini sedap. 
- Hei.

468
00:32:23,691 --> 00:32:25,443
Kamu belanja ini saja?

469
00:32:25,944 --> 00:32:27,654
- Begitu? 
- Makan sajalah.

470
00:32:29,113 --> 00:32:30,239
Aduhai.

471
00:32:31,240 --> 00:32:32,575
Apa pun…

472
00:32:32,659 --> 00:32:36,746
adik bongsu kita beli aiskrim 
dengan wang hadiah kejohanan.

473
00:32:36,829 --> 00:32:38,039
Abang bangga.

474
00:32:39,082 --> 00:32:42,043
Baek-du. Abang tonton perlawanan kamu.

475
00:32:42,126 --> 00:32:44,045
- Kamu nampak berbeza. 
- Betul.

476
00:32:44,545 --> 00:32:47,757
Ada orang beritahu saya sesuatu 
dan ia buat saya sedar.

477
00:32:47,840 --> 00:32:49,884
Siapa? Teman wanita kamu?

478
00:32:49,968 --> 00:32:52,679
Jangan buat-buat tak tahu. Abang nampak.

479
00:32:53,221 --> 00:32:55,056
Apa maksud abang? Nampak apa?

480
00:32:55,139 --> 00:32:57,433
Abang tak pasti kamu bercinta atau tidak,

481
00:32:57,517 --> 00:32:59,560
tapi yang pastinya kamu ada hubungan

482
00:32:59,644 --> 00:33:01,896
dengan seorang gadis, bukan?

483
00:33:02,522 --> 00:33:03,815
Saya…

484
00:33:04,565 --> 00:33:05,400
Betulkah?

